Created Topic model and API endpoints for knowledge organization system. Migrated agent_documents from string topics to FK relationships.

Implementation:
- Created Topic model with id, title, description, icon, linked_project_id, auto_created, created_at, updated_at
- Replaced agent_documents.topic (string) with topic_id (FK to topics)
- Added topic_id FK to research_requests  
- Created 8 API endpoints: GET/POST /api/topics, GET/PUT/DELETE /api/topics/{id}, GET /api/topics/{id}/documents
- Migration script created 13 topics from existing distinct topic strings, updated 69 agent documents
- Added Pydantic schemas: Topic, TopicCreate, TopicUpdate
- Updated AgentDocument and ResearchRequest schemas to use topic_id

Tests: 15 tests passed (100% success rate)
- Covered CRUD operations, validation, pagination, duplicate prevention
- Tested topic-documents relationship endpoint
- Verified auto_created flag functionality
